<preface id="idg-cmmoperator-cmmoperator-about-c-about-xml-1">
 <title>About this Manual</title>
 <para>
  This manual describes how system operators can install, operate, maintain,
  and monitor FUJITSU ServerView <phrase>Cloud Monitoring Manager</phrase> -
  hereafter referred to as <phrase>Cloud Monitoring Manager</phrase>
  (<phrase>CMM</phrase>).
 </para>
 <para>
  The manual is structured as follows:
